title: Star Wars Jedi: Survivor - How to Kill the Rancor
description:
The Rancor is one of the toughest optional battles you'll find early on in Star Wars Jedi: Survivor, but if you're determined and want to take him out right away, here are tips on what to do against each of his attacks and some general strategy to keep in mind for the fight.

title: Heretic's Fork - Exclusive Trailer
description:
Check out this exclusive trailer for Heretic's Fork, an upcoming tower defense game featuring deckbuilding mechanics. Build a hellish tower and use cards to fortify your base and acquire new weapons to withstand the rampage of sinners. Learn more about Heretic's Fork here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2181610/Heretics_Fork/ 

Heretic's Fork consists of nine departments, each representing a different circle of Hell, and you must help solve the issue of overpopulation by keeping heretics in check.
